name: Chained Cars Extraordinary Fas
description:
Chained Cars Extraordinary Fast is a chained cars racing endless runner .The task is to control your car with the speed of your chained AI car. Maintain very proper speed to avoid aggressive crashes. Here you can find how difficult the city car driving will be, with more speed breakers and road diversions. We added some extra off-road obstacles to make your chained car ride really tougher.
Features:
- Realistic Car physics
- Awesome 3d environment
- Multiple chained cars
- Super luxury cars to chose and drive
- Super luxury cars to choose and drive.
- Vehicles traffic rush on asphalt city roads.
